title: Vegan Bunker
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Pizza, Western, Fast food, Take-out, Bakery, Chilean
description: Vegan restaurant and coffee shop, opened Oct 2012 at previous location Av. Blanco Encalada 2479 and moved to this larger and brighter space in 2014. Offers a menu-of-the-day plus vegan fast food like pizza, veggie burgers, as well as raw options and various baked goods and vegan cakes.
